Package org.apache.axis.ime

Interface Summary
MessageExchange Represents the boundary interface through which messages are exchanged.
MessageExchangeConstants  
MessageExchangeCorrelator Used for correlating outbound/inbound messages.
MessageExchangeEvent The base interface for all MessageExchange events, such as message receipt notification, delivery acknowledgement, exception notification, and status.
MessageExchangeEventListener The base interface to be extended by all MessageExchangeEvent listeners.
MessageExchangeFactory  
MessageExchangeLifecycle Interface that may be provided by MessageExchange impl's to allow users to control the lifecycle of the "stuff" going on under the covers
